#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Today's topic is about spending one-on-one time with our teens. \n"
"\n"
"Being a parent can be so hard. Sometimes it feels like our teens never listen to us.\n"
"\n"
"But science shows that spending just a few minutes each day of focused one-on-one time with your teen helps build trust and love."
msgstr ""
"Mada ya leo inahusu kutumia muda wa pamoja wawili na vijana wetu.\n"
"\n"
"Kuwa mzazi kunaweza kuwa kugumu sana. Wakati mwingine inaonekana kama vijana wetu hawatusikilizi kabisa.\n"
"\n"
"Lakini sayansi inaonyesha kwamba kutumia dakika chache tu kila siku za muda wa pekee na kijana wako kunasaidia kujenga uaminifu na upendo."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Why is spending one-on-one time with your teens important? Click play to learn"
msgstr "Kwa nini ni muhimu kutumia muda wa pamoja na vijana wako? Bonyeza kucheza ili kujifunza"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Hello.\n"
"\n"
"Our topic today is one-on-one time with our children.\n"
"\n"
"It is important to spend time with our children so that they can get to understand us, and for us to get an opportunity to understand them.\n"
"\n"
"Remember, a family with good understanding lives in harmony."
msgstr ""
"Habari!\n"
"\n"
"Mada yetu ya leo inahusu kuzungumza na watoto wetu mkiwa wawili.\n"
"\n"
"Ni muhimu kutumia muda tukiwa na watoto wetu ili waweze kutuelewa, na sisi kupata fursa ya kuwaelewa.\n"
"\n"
"Kumbuka, familia inayoelewana vizuri huishi kwa utulivu."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Let's discuss, what is one-on-one time?\n"
"\n"
"One-on-one time is when you focus on your teens, without distractions like TVs or phones. Let your teens take lead in choosing what you do or talk about.\n"
"\n"
"It is great if you can spend fifteen minutes a day together, but even five minutes a day is really good."
msgstr ""
"Ngoja  tujadili, nini maana ya kutumia muda wa pamoja?\n"
"\n"
"Kutumia muda wa pamoja ni pale wakati unayowazingatia vijana wako, bila usumbufu kama televisheni au simu. Waachie vijana wako kuongoza katika kuchagua kile mnachofanya au kuzungumzia.\n"
"\n"
"Ni jambo zuri kama unaweza kutumia dakika 15 kwa siku pamoja kijana, lakini hata dakika 5 kwa siku pia ni vizuri sana."

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.media_female_1.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Hear how one-on-one time helped @data.characters.media_female_1.name and her teen"
msgstr "Sikia jinsi gani kutumia muda wa pamoja kulivyomsaidia @data.characters.media_female_1.name na kijana wake"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"When I first heard I had to spend One-on-One Time with my teen, it was hard for me. I did not know when to do it or what to say. I did not want to spoil my teen so that he thinks we have to do everything together.\n"
"\n"
"But I really wanted to build my relationship with my teen and I wanted him to open up about what was troubling him. So we tried the One-on-One Time.\n"
"\n"
"First, it felt weird, but it turned out to be fun! Now we watch his TV programme together and we chat about it. And we can even talk about how my son is changing into adolescence and even about girlfriends and those things!"
msgstr ""
"Wakati niliposikia kwa mara ya kwanza kuwa ni lazima nitumie muda wa pamoja na kijana wangu, ilikuwa ngumu kwangu. Sikujuwa ni lini nifanye hivyo au niseme nini. Sikutaka kumzoesha kijana wangu hadi afikirie kuwa tunapaswa kufanya kila kitu pamoja.\n"
"\n"
"Lakini nilitaka sana kujenga uhusiano wangu na kijana wangu na nilitaka afunguke kuhusu kile kinachomsumbua. Kwa hiyo tulijaribu kuwa na muda wa pamoja wawili.\n"
"\n"
"Mwanzo, lilihisi kuwa ni jambo la ajabu, lakini baadaye likawa la kufurahisha! Sasa tunaangalia kipindi chake cha runinga pamoja na tunazungumza kuhusu hilo. Na hata tunaweza kuzungumza kuhusu jinsi mwanangu anavyobadilika kuwa katika umri wa ujana, hata kuhusu wasichana na mambo kama hayo!\n"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Let's think of ways to spend time with your teen.\n"
"\n"
"It may take some time to get used to one-on-one time, but the more you do it, the better it gets!\n"
"\n"
"You are an amazing parent for trying this."
msgstr ""
"Wacha tufikirie njia za kutumia muda na kijana wako.\n"
"\n"
"Inaweza kuchukua muda kuzoea kutumia muda wa pamoja, lakini kadri unavyozidi kufanya, ndivyo unavyokuwa bora zaidi!\n"
"\n"
"Wewe ni mzazi mahiri kwa kujaribu hili."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "What could you do to spend one-on-one time with your teen?"
msgstr "Je, unaweza kuutumiaje muda wa pamoja na kijana wako mkiwa wawili?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Walk to the shops"
msgstr "Tembea kwenda madukani"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Play a game/sport"
msgstr "Kucheza mchezo"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Have tea after school"
msgstr "Kunywa chai akitoka shule"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Prepare dinner"
msgstr "Andaa chakula cha usiku"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Eat breakfast/lunch/dinner"
msgstr "Kula kifungua kinywa/mlo wa mchana/mlo wa usiku"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Great idea! \n"
"\n"
"Feel like you have NO TIME and you are exhausted? Remember to also think of ways that do not take up extra time, like doing a chore together while chatting."
msgstr ""
"Wazo zuri!\n"
"\n"
"Unahisi huna MUDA na umechoka? Kumbuka pia kufikiria njia ambazo hazihitaji muda wa ziada, kama kufanya kazi ya nyumbani pamoja huku mkiwa mnaongea."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Here are some skills to help guide you in spending one-on-one time with your teen!"
msgstr "Hapa kuna baadhi ya ujuzi wa kukusaidia katika wakati wa pamoja na kijana wako!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "DAY"
msgstr "SIKU"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Try to do it every day. \n"
"\n"
"Find 5 minutes (or more!) each day when your teen does not have something else they want to do."
msgstr ""
"Jaribu kufanya hivi kila siku.\n"
"\n"
"Tafuta dakika 5 (au zaidi!) kila siku wakati kijana wako hana kitu kingine anachotaka kufanya."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "PLAY"
msgstr "CHEZA"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Let your teen choose.\n"
"\n"
"Tell your teen that you would like to spend some time with them and that they can choose what to do or talk about. They might think this is weird at first, but they will come to enjoy this time with you!"
msgstr ""
"Muache kijana wako achague.\n"
"\n"
"Mwambie kijana wako kwamba ungependa kutumia muda pamoja naye na kwamba anaweza kuchagua cha kufanya au cha kuzungumzia. Mwanzoni, anaweza kuona kuwa hili ni jambo la ajabu, lakini baadaye atafurahia muda huu wa kuwa na wewe!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "STAY"
msgstr "KAA"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Focus on your teen.\n"
"\n"
"Switch off the TV and put phones aside. Look at your teen. Nod or say ‚ÄúI see‚Äù to show that you are really paying attention. Accept what they say without judging them."
msgstr ""
"Weka umakini kwa kijana wako.\n"
"\n"
"Zima runinga na weka simu kando. Mtazame kijana wako. Fanya ishara kwa kichwa au sema \"ndiyo\" ili kuonyesha kuwa unampa mkazo. Kubali anachosema bila kumhukumu."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Spending one-on-one time with your teen can be hard to plan. Here are some easy ideas that worked for other parents."
msgstr "Kupanga muda wa pamoja na na kijana wako inaweza kuwa gumu. Hapa kuna baadhi ya mawazo rahisi ambayo yamewasaidia wazazi wengine."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"**Ideas for one-on-one time with your teen:**\n"
"- Walk to the shops\n"
"- Play a game/sport\n"
"- Do a chore together\n"
"- Prepare dinner\n"
"- Eat breakfast/lunch/dinner\n"
"- Have tea after school\n"
"- Watch a TV show\n"
"- Review homework\n"
"- Chat before bedtime\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"**Remember to use your new skills:**\n"
"üìÖ **DAY**: try to do it every day,\n"
"‚öΩ **PLAY**: let your teen choose how to spend one-on-one time, and \n"
"üéØ **STAY**: be focused on your teen!"
msgstr ""
"**Mawazo ya kutumia muda wa pamoja na kijana wako.**\n"
"- Kutembea kwenda dukani\n"
"- Kucheza magemu au michezo\n"
"- Kufanya kazi ya nyumbani pamoja\n"
"- Kuandaa chakula cha jioni\n"
"- Kula kifungua kinywa / chakula cha mchana / chakula cha jioni\n"
"- Kunywa chai baada ya shule\n"
"- Kuangalia kipindi cha televisheni\n"
"- Kupitia kazi za nyumbani\n"
"- Kuongea kabla ya kwenda kulala\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"**Kumbuka kutumia stadi zako mpya:**\n"
"üìÖ **Siku**: jaribu kufanya kila siku,\n"
"‚öΩ **Cheza**: waache vijana wako wachague jinsi ya kutumia muda wa pamoja, na\n"
"üéØ **Kaa**: zingatia kijana wako!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "This week's home activity is to spend 5-15 minutes of one-on-one time with your teen, every day that you can."
msgstr "Shughuli ya nyumbani ya wiki hii ni kutumia dakika 5-15 za pamoja na kijana wako, kila siku utakayoweza."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Can you spend one-on-one time with your teen this week?"
msgstr "Je, unaweza kutumia muda wa pamoja na kijana wako wiki hii?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Yes"
msgstr "Ndiyo"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "That's great! Parents who spend focused one-on-one time with their teens can build trust and love!"
msgstr "Hiyo ni nzuri sana! Wazazi wanaotumia muda wa  pamoja kwa makini na vijana wao wanaweza kujenga uaminifu na upendo!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "I think so"
msgstr ""
"Nafikiri hivyo\n"
"Nafikiri hivyo"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "You can do it! Try spending just a few minutes each day with your teen. Remember that you can always think of ways that do not take up extra time, like walking to the shop or preparing dinner together."
msgstr "Unaweza kufanya hivyo! Jaribu kutumia dakika chache tu kila siku na kijana wako. Kumbuka kuwa daima unaweza kufikiria njia zisizohitaji muda wa ziada, kama kutembea kwenda dukani au kuandaa chakula cha jioni pamoja."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "No"
msgstr "Hapana"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "That's okay. Spending focused time with your teen will become easier as you build a routine. At first, you can try to think of ways that do not take up extra time, like doing a chore together."
msgstr "Hii ni sawa. Kutumia muda wa pamoja na kijana wako kutakuwa rahisi zaidi kadri mnavyojenga ratiba ya pamoja. Mwanzoni, unaweza kujaribu kufikiria njia ambazo hazihitaji muda wa ziada, kama kufanya kazi ya nyumbani pamoja."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Remember, spending even a few minutes of one-on-one time with your teen each day can strengthen your relationship and build trust. \n"
"\n"
"Listening closely and sharing small moments helps teens feel loved and supported."
msgstr ""
"Kumbuka, kutumia hata dakika chache tu za muda wa pamoja na kijana wako kila siku kunaweza kuimarisha uhusiano wenu na kujenga uaminifu.\n"
"\n"
"Sikiliza kwa makini na kushirikisha nyakati fulani nzuri huwasaidia vijana kujisikia kupendwa na kuungwa mkono."

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.media_daughter_1.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Here's what @data.characters.media_daughter_1.name has to say about one-on-one time with her mother"
msgstr "Hapa kuna @data.characters.media_daughter_1.name anachosema kuhusu muda wa pamoja na mama yake"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"When my mother asked to spend time with me, I thought ‚ÄúMaybe something is wrong, maybe she is sick.‚Äù But she said ‚ÄúNo, I just want to spend time.‚Äù I was sceptical, but I accepted.\n"
"\n"
"She asked me what I like doing. It was strange and I was not comfortable, because she never ever spent time with me on my own.\n"
"\n"
"The more she kept on trying and we spent this time together, it felt really nice. She got to share her own childhood with me, things I never heard before. That helped me to also share what is going on in my life. We even talk about boyfriends and about problems I have. I know I can talk to my mother now."
msgstr ""
"Mama yangu alipoomba kukaa nami, nilifikiri ‚ÄúLabda kuna tatizo, labda ni mgonjwa.‚Äù Lakini alisema, \"Hapana, nataka tu kakaa nami.\" Nilikuwa na shaka, lakini nilikubali.\n"
"\n"
"Aliniuliza ninapenda kufanya nini. Ilikuwa ya kushangaza na sikuwa na raha, kwa sababu hakuwahi kutumia wakati na mimi peke yangu.\n"
"\n"
"Kadiri alivyozidi kujaribu na kuwa na wakati huu pamoja, nilijisikia vizuri sana. Alnishirikisha maisha yake ya utotoni, mambo ambayo sikuwahi kuyasikia hapo awali. Hilo lilinisaidia pia kushiriki kile kinachoendelea katika maisha yangu. Tunazungumza hata juu ya wapenzi na shida nilizonazo. Najua naweza kuzungumza na mama yangu sasa."

